# IPFS setup tutorial

## Connect to your server

Using ssh, connect to your server:
  ssh -L 8080:localhost:8080 -L 5001:localhost:5001 root@server_ip

## Configure your IPFS

IPFS documentation can be found at https://ipfs.io/docs/getting-started/
The IPFS daemon is already running, follow the instructions depending on your
needs.
